d projects across repositories\",\"Read organization, team, repo, and user metadata\"],\"consumer_bullets\":null,\"connected_bullets\":null,\"developer\":\"Microsoft\",\"website_url\":\"https://github.com\",\"support_url\":\"https://support.github.com\",\"documentation_url\":\"https://docs.github.com/en/rest\",\"footnote\":null,\"setup_steps\":[]},\"display_categories\":[\"Developer\"],\"is_popular\":true,\"popularity\":null,\"is_created_by_current_user\":false,\"is_user_selectable\":true,\"is_premium\":false,\"is_consumer_only\":false,\"supported_exec_envs\":[],\"template_source_id\":null,\"extra_config\":null,\"org_disabled\":null,\"setup_descriptor\":null,\"viewer_setup_state\":null,\"family_info\":null,\"provider\":\"direct\",\"user_connections\":[{\"connection_uuid\":\"a5d16174-cfb8-4d07-be22-26e5a64c3dbb\",\"connection_display_name\":\"vb.mrme00@gmail.com\",\"has_required_scopes\":true,\"file_picker_credentials\":null,\"account_identifier\":\"vb.mrme00@gmail.com\"}],\"migration\":null},{\"id\":\"health\",\"display_name\":\"Health\",\"description\":\"Access your health and wellness data\",\"type\":\"other\",\"auth_type\":\"none\",\"icon_url\":null,\"capabilities\":{},\"connection_type\":null,\"query_rate_limit\":{\"monthly_limit\":null,\"remaining\":null},\"source_scope\":\"global\",\"auth_scope\":\"individual\",\"created_by_org_id\":null,\"created_by_user_id\":null,\"is_template\":false,\"required_fields\":null,\"source_details\":{\"tagline\":null,\"bullets\":[],\"consumer_bullets\":null,\"connected_bullets\":null,\"developer\":null,\"website_url\":null,\"support_url\":null,\"documentation_url\":null,\"footnote\":null,\"setup_steps\":[]},\"display_categories\":[],\"is_popular\":false,\"popularity\":null,\"is_created_by_current_user\":false,\"is_user_selectable\":true,\"is_premium\":false,\"is_consumer_only\":false,\"supported_exec_envs\":[],\"template_source_id\":null,\"extra_config\":null,\"org_disabled\":null,\"setup_descriptor\":null,\"viewer_setup_state\":null,\"family_info\":null,\"provider\":null,\"user_connections\":[],\"migration\":null},{\"id\":\"midpage\",\"display_name\":\"Midpage\",\"description\":\"A law library for AI - search, analyze, and cite US case law with confidence\",\"type\":\"remote_mcp\",\"auth_type\":\"none\",\"icon_url\":\"https://r2cdn.perplexity.ai/sources/midpage/icon.svg\",\"capabilities\":{},\"connection_type\":null,\"query_rate_limit\":{\"monthly_limit\":5,\"remaining\":5},\"source_scope\":\"global\",\"auth_scope\":\"individual\",\"created_by_org_id\":null,\"created_by_user_id\":null,\"is_template\":false,\"required_fields\":null,\"source_details\":{\"tagline\":\"A law library for AI — search, analyze, and cite US case law with confidence.\",\"bullets\":[\"Search US case law across all federal and state courts using keywords, natural language questions, boolean queries, or legal propositions, with filters for jurisdiction, date, and publication status\",\"Find quotable passages within any opinion using fast keyword search — useful for quickly checking whether a case is relevant before committing to deeper analysis\",\"Analyze opinions with AI to extract verified holdings, cite-ready propositions with pinpoint citations, verbatim quotes, scope limitations, and citator treatment (positive/negative/caution/neutral) — required before citing any case\",\"Check citator status to confirm whether a case is still good law, with treatment data and citation counts drawn from a graph of 90 million links between cases\",\"Generate properly cited legal writing with Bluebook-formatted citations and shareable Midpage links that point to exact sentence ranges in the opinion text\"],\"consumer_bullets\":null,\"connected_bullets\":null,\"developer\":null,\"website_url\":\"https://www.midpage.ai/\",\"support_url\":\"https://www.midpage.ai/contact-sales\",\"documentation_url\":\"https://www.midpage.ai/data\",\"footnote\":null,\"setup_steps\":[]},\"display_categories\":[\"Legal\"],\"is_popular\":false,\"popularity\":null,\"is_created_by_current_user\":false,\"is_user_selectable\":true,\"is_premium\":true,\"is_consumer_only\":false,\"supported_exec_envs\":[],\"template_source_id\":null,\"extra_config\":null,\"org_disabled\":null,\"setup_descriptor\":null,\"viewer_setup_state\":null,\"family_info\":null,\"provider\":\"direct\",\"user_connections\":[],\"migration\":null},{\"id\":\"nejm\",\"display_name\":\"NEJM\",\"description\":\"The New England Journal of Medicine, or NEJM, is a long-running, peer-reviewed medical journal focused on publishing rigorously vetted medical research, clinical reviews, and case-based educational content for physicians and clinicians. It positions itself as a trusted source for essential findings in medicine and clinical best practices, with a history spanning more than 200 years.\",\"type\":\"other\",\"auth_type\":\"none\",\"icon_url\":\"https://r2cdn.perplexity.ai/sources/nejm/icon.svg\",\"capabilities\":{},\"connection_type\":null,\"query_rate_limit\":null,\"source_scope\":\"global\",\"auth_scope\":\"individual\",\"created_by_org_id\":null,\"created_by_user_id\":null,\"is_template\":false,\"required_fields\":null,\"source_details\":{\"tagline\":null,\"bullets\":[\" Trusted medical research source: NEJM publishes rigorously peer-reviewed medical research and essential findings for clinicians .\",\"Built for physicians and care teams: Its content supports physicians, clinicians, and patient care through research, reviews, clinical cases, and interactive education.\",\"Deep medical legacy: NEJM has been part of medical publishing for more than 200 years and has covered major advances from anesthesia to modern cancer and cardiology treatments.\"],\"consumer_bullets\":null,\"connected_bullets\":null,\"developer\":null,\"website_url\":\"https://www.nejm.org/\",\"support_url\":null,\"documentation_url\":null,\"footnote\":null,\"setup_steps\":[]},\"display_categories\":[],\"is_popular\":false,\"popularity\":null,\"is_created_by_current_user\":false,\